<div id="dashboard">
  <h1 class="heading-large">Welcome to the FCERM project funding service</h1>

  <p class="lede">This is your home page. You can review and update any existing project proposal and start a new project proposal.</p>

  <div class="panel panel-border-wide">
    <p>If you want to request FCERM project funding for next year, you must apply before the submission deadline of 31st July 2017.</p>
  </div>

  <p>If you need to make a change to your project proposal after you've submitted it, for example because you made a mistake, you'll need to update and resubmit your project proposal before the submission deadline.</p>

  <p>If you need to make a change after the submission deadline, you can still update and resubmit your project proposal but any changes won't be considered as part of the current assessment period.</p>
  <p>If you have any questions about the projects listed here, contact your <%= link_to "local partnership and strategic overview officer", t(".contact_link"), rel: "external", target: "_blank" %>.</p>

  <div>
    <%= link_to t('create_a_new_project_label'), pafs_core.new_project_path, class: "button" %>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-medium">Your existing project proposals</h2>
    <table class="dashboard">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th scope="col">Reference no.</th>
          <th scope="col">Project name</th>
          <th scope="col">RMA</th>
          <th scope="col">Location</th>
          <th scope="col">Type</th>
          <th scope="col">Status</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% @projects.each do |project| %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= link_to project.reference_number, pafs_core.project_path(project), class: "project-link" %></td>
            <td><%= project.name %></td>
            <td>Bristol city council</td>
            <td>BS4 8NP</td>
            <td>1-6 yrs</td>
            <td>Approved</td>
          </tr>
        <% end %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>
</div>
